Air New Zealand is usually very careful not to disturb passengers at night. This crew was clearly self-obsessed and noisy. Not my kind of crew. What was even tackier was the way air New Zealand took the feedback. They just sent out a form letter. When we travelled through Portugal, no matter where we went, I would order sardines. And that was pretty much the same story here in Greece. I just adore sardines. Most of the time we got an amazing array of vegetables, beans etc. But when sardines were available, that’s what I had to order.
